summary: This document appears to be a certificate of resolutions for a Limited Liability Company (LLC) related to Deutsche Bank Wealth Management. It outlines the authority of designated individuals to manage accounts and execute agreements on behalf of the company. The document emphasizes the responsibilities and powers of the authorized signers in relation to the bank's services.
keyFacts: The document certifies the authority of certain individuals to manage accounts for a Limited Liability Company.
It outlines the responsibilities of the authorized signers in relation to Deutsche Bank.
The document includes provisions for the bank to accept instructions from authorized signers regarding account management.
